<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CareerAIPlus - Personalized Learning Roadmap</title>
    <style>
      body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: black;
    color: white;
}
header {
  background-color: #a9a9a9;
  padding: 20px 25px;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: bold;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.logo svg {
  width: 25px;
  height: 25px;
  margin-right: 7px;
}

nav {
  color: black;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

nav ul {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  display: flex;
}

nav ul li {
  margin: 0 15px;
}

nav ul li a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: black;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}

nav ul li a:hover {
  color: rgb(239, 239, 239);
}

nav ul li a.active {
  color: white;
  /* background-color: white; */
  font-weight: bolder;
  /* border: 1px solid white; */
  /* padding: 8px;
      border-radius: 25px; */
}

.hamburger {
        display: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-around;
        width: 30px;
        height: 25px;
        background: none;
        border: none;
        z-index: 1001;
    }

    .hamburger-line {
        width: 100%;
        height: 3px;
        background-color: black;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
.roadmap {
    background-color: black;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
.course-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-evenly;
    padding: 20px;
}
.course-card {
    background-color: #222;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    width: 300px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.15s;
}
.course-card:hover{
  transform: scale(1.1);
  transition: transform 0.15s;
}
.course-card img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
}
.explore-btn {
    background-color: red;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
}
.explore-btn:hover{
  background-color: darkred;
}
footer {
  background-color: #a9a9a9;
  text-align: left;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-top: 50px;
  color: black;
}
.footer-content {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
}
footer .footer-links a {
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  color: black;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
footer .footer-links a:hover {
  color: rgb(239, 239, 239);
  font-weight: bold;
}
.footer-links h3 {
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 1.15rem;
}
.footer-links p {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}
.footer-links {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}
@media(max-width : 768px){
  nav ul {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #a9a9a9;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 100;
}

nav ul li {
    margin: 15px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

.hamburger {
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1001;
}

/* Hamburger menu animation */
.hamburger.active .hamburger-line:nth-child(1) {
    transform: rotate(45deg) translate(5px, 5px);
}

.hamburger.active .hamburger-line:nth-child(2) {
    opacity: 0;
}

.hamburger.active .hamburger-line:nth-child(3) {
    transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(5px, -5px);
}

nav ul.show {
    display: flex;
}
.course-container{
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 0 20px;
  gap: 25px;
}
.footer-links h3{
  font-size: 0.90rem;
}
.footer-links a {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
}
.footer-links p {
  font-size: 0.80rem;
}
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', {title: ' learning roadmaps', page: 'assessment'}) %>
    <main>
      
        <section class="roadmap">
            <h2>Your Personalized Learning Roadmap</h2>
            <p>Based on your career assessment, here are your recommended learning paths.</p>
            <div class="course-container">
                <div class="course-card">
                    <img src="./img/courseDemoImg/demo1.jpeg" alt="Data Science Specialization">
                    <h3>Data Science Specialization</h3>
                    <p>Offered by Coursera, this path provides foundational skills in data science.</p>
                    <button class="explore-btn">Explore Course</button>
                </div>
                <div class="course-card">
                    <img src="./img/courseDemoImg/demo3.jpeg" alt="Advanced Mathematics">
                    <h3>Advanced Mathematics</h3>
                    <p>Enhance your math skills with Khan Academy's interactive courses.</p>
                    <button class="explore-btn">Explore Course</button>
                </div>
                <div class="course-card">
                    <img src="./img/courseDemoImg/demo2.jpeg" alt="Graphic Design Masterclass">
                    <h3>Graphic Design Masterclass</h3>
                    <p>Udemy's comprehensive course for aspiring graphic designers.</p>
                    <button class="explore-btn">Explore Course</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
      <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
